author: @5b57

simpleText: It depends on your learning methods, your focus, time and generally how well does it all stick. It's not impossible, but very small percentage of folk will be able to do it, 6 months is really not much. And even if, those 6 months will get you the absolute basics. Don't give yourself any static deadlines with something as complex as AI/ML. Rather, make a milestone calendar and get advice from someone experianced. Believe me it helps a lot. Assess your progress in intervals, and grind and apply your knowledge iteratively, meaning increase the size and the complexity of your projects in small steps.
